# Cloudflare Pages 重定向规则
# HTTP 到 HTTPS 重定向 - 强制所有 HTTP 请求重定向到 HTTPS
http://recipe-easy.com/* https://recipe-easy.com/:splat 301!
http://www.recipe-easy.com/* https://recipe-easy.com/:splat 301!

# 确保 www 和非 www 都重定向到主域名
https://www.recipe-easy.com/* https://recipe-easy.com/:splat 301!

# 保持末尾斜杠一致性
# 确保所有URL都有末尾斜杠（可选配置） 